msgid "In the season of life in which I was exposed to the Hearth's Fire, into deep contemplation did I withdraw to ponder the nature of truth. I sharpened my mind as my blade and defined the principles I would honor for all my future days.\n\nWith Tava's blessing, the sword-singer must do the same to achieve Mastery of Wisdom."
